::Prowl::

Prowl swears silently as he recieves Shocker's transmission. "No, you're 
not," he replies silently. He was slowly losing his temper. He was under 
enough pressure not to have to deal with disobedient troops, "You're the only 
ones that could make us get captured again. Now retreat, that's an order! 
We'll meet up with you later."

He says, continuing to walk down the halls of the Alliance base, seeing Iron 
Raptor and Tavatron fall into step behind him.
